# Stray root-level Python backend dirs that live in this repo for historical
# reasons — NOT part of the Next.js frontend. Critically, a root /app directory
# shadows src/app for Next.js App Router directory detection (Next.js prefers
# <root>/app over <root>/src/app when both exist), which silently builds zero
# routes if this dir is present in the build context. Must stay excluded.
/app
/backend
.env*
!.env.example
npm-debug.log*
test-results
playwright-report
e2e
data/
sessions/
*.db
*.session
.backup
*.log
